works.description: Kate Middleton has already left her family home for the last time as a singleton, and she will be spending the night before the wedding day tomorrow at the Goring Hotel in central London. She will be staying there with her sister and chief bridesmaid Pippa and parents Michael and Carole. Since she isn’t a commoner anymore, we don’t expect her to stay in a regular hotel room. The royal bride-to-be will moved into the five-star £5,000-a-night ($8,500-a-night) Royal Apartment on the top floor of the Goring Hotel.
